        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "When inline MathLive widgets are enabled, inline MathJax in the editor is always hidden so clicks reach the widget (otherwise MathJax sits on top and the first click dismisses editing). When widgets are off, this only toggles hiding MathJax for $…$ in Live Preview.",
          "target": "当启用内联 MathLive 小部件时，编辑器中的内联 MathJax 始终隐藏，以便点击能到达小部件（否则 MathJax 会覆盖在上面，第一次点击会关闭编辑）。当小部件关闭时，此选项仅切换在实时预览中隐藏 $…$ 的 MathJax。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "When block MathLive widgets are enabled, block MathJax in the editor is always hidden for the same reason as inline (click-through). When block widgets are off, this only toggles hiding MathJax for $$…$$ in Live Preview.",
